"photo-credit-creditor\"\u003eCourtesy of Dale Arden Chong\u003c/span\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003cp\u003eThe editor wearing the XT-6 sneakers.\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"9\"\u003eNext up on my list was the \u003ca href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com?id=74968X1525074\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salomon.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2Fxt-whisper-li8028.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-vars-ga-outbound-link=\"https://www.salomon.com/en-us/shop/product/xt-whisper-li8028.html\" data-vars-ga-ux-element=\"Hyperlink\" data-vars-ga-call-to-action=\"XT-Whisper\" data-vars-ga-product-id=\"7e4490ba-672e-4b4a-83a1-f6c5e7ea4ce9\" data-node-id=\"9.1\" data-href=\"https://www.salomon.com/en-us/shop/product/xt-whisper-li8028.html\" data-product-url=\"https://www.salomon.com/en-us/shop/product/xt-whisper-li8028.html\" data-affiliate=\"true\" data-affiliate-url=\"https://go.redirectingat.com?id=74968X1525074\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salomon.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2Fxt-whisper-li8028.html\" data-affiliate-network=\"{\u0026#34;afflink_redirect\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;/_p/afflink/tXQB/salomon-s-en-us-shop-xt-whisper-li8028\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;site_id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;530bacd4-96b2-4cfe-a9a6-1fbd7c749e22\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;network\u0026#34;:{\u0026#34;name\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Skimlinks\u0026#34;}}\" data-vars-ga-product-price=\"$0.00\" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id=\"b763a805-4ea5-457b-863b-757bbc8e8ac4\" data-vars-ga-link-treatment=\"(not set) | (not set)\"\u003eXT-Whisper\u003c/a\u003e. This might be the buzziest of Salomon’s sportstyle silhouettes at the moment. Its latest Sandy Liang launch featured a pink-ified version of what I’m dubbing the brand’s take on the dad shoe. This is no exaggeration: These are the sneakers made me forget about any others. Available in a number of colorways, the XT-Whisper has become my go-to option. I’ll slip these on when I’m running a quick errand, jumping on a plane, or even heading to the office.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"10\"\u003eThe third style I opted to try was the \u003ca href=\"https://go.redirectingat.com?id=74968X1525074\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salomon.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2Fxt-4-og-li3335.html%23color%3D76393\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" data-vars-ga-outbound-link=\"https://www.salomon.com/en-us/shop/product/xt-4-og-li3335.html#color=76393\" data-vars-ga-ux-element=\"Hyperlink\" data-vars-ga-call-to-action=\"XT-4 OG\" data-vars-ga-product-id=\"b40e3b29-6223-484a-bff5-ecf9e41b8e3c\" data-node-id=\"10.1\" data-href=\"https://www.salomon.com/en-us/shop/product/xt-4-og-li3335.html#color=76393\" data-product-url=\"https://www.salomon.com/en-us/shop/product/xt-4-og-li3335.html#color=76393\" data-affiliate=\"true\" data-affiliate-url=\"https://go.redirectingat.com?id=74968X1525074\u0026amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.salomon.com%2Fen-us%2Fshop%2Fproduct%2Fxt-4-og-li3335.html%23color%3D76393\" data-affiliate-network=\"{\u0026#34;afflink_redirect\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;/_p/afflink/tXQJ/salomon-s-en-us-shop-xt-4-og-li3335-color-76393\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;site_id\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;530bacd4-96b2-4cfe-a9a6-1fbd7c749e22\u0026#34;,\u0026#34;network\u0026#34;:{\u0026#34;name\u0026#34;:\u0026#34;Skimlinks\u0026#34;}}\" data-vars-ga-product-price=\"$0.00\" data-vars-ga-product-retailer-id=\"82b70dbe-99c4-4d7a-81f5-c259a9e8d4a3\" data-vars-ga-link-treatment=\"(not set) | (not set)\"\u003eXT-4 OG\u003c/a\u003e. This silhouette feels a little more futuristic in aesthetics, but it’s also one of the most iconic styles the brand has to offer, with a design that feels both technical and visually pleasing. These felt like the most “streetwear-ready” style, given that it’s just a little chunkier than the others, but I felt they were equally great for my routines.\u003c/p\u003e\u003cdiv role=\"region\" aria-label=\"carousel\" data-embed=\"embed-gallery\" data-lazy-id=\"P0-12\" data-node-id=\"11\"\u003e\u003cp\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/img-7656-67eee0d95608d.jpeg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=480:* 640w, https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/img-7656-67eee0d95608d.jpeg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=980:* 980w\" alt=\"salomon sneakers wear test\" src=\"https://hips.hearstapps.com/hmg-prod/images/img-7656-67eee0d95608d.jpeg?crop=1xw:1xh;center,top\u0026amp;resize=980:*\" title=\"salomon sneakers wear test\" width=\"1600\" height=\"2000\" decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\"/\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\u003cfigcaption data-theme-key=\"photo-credit-figcaption\"\u003e\u003c/figcaption\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003cp data-journey-content=\"true\" data-node-id=\"12\"\u003eI am, without a doubt, a Salomon evangelist—and honestly, it’s not hard to be. The colorways are intriguing enough to catch the eyes of nearly anyone (including my therapist, who added the XT-Whispers to her wish list after seeing mine), as well as my fashion-curious friends. On top of that, the fit and comfort feel unmatched. So, I just have one question for you: If you don’t already have a pair...what are you doing?!\u003c/p\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
